cz.cuni.mff.kocur.server

Class RequestArguments

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.server.RequestArguments

  • public class RequestArguments
extends java.lang.Object
    This class should represent a object, that stores all necessary information about an incoming request. It should store the url, incoming message and code of the request (UPDATE, UPDATEDIRE ..).
    Author:
    kocur

        public Response set(java.lang.String[] uriFields)

        Parameters:

        Returns a response, that is set to passed if everything went according to plan. Else there is a message attached to it with error.

      • checkMethod

        private void checkMethod(Response res,
                         RequestHandler.CODE method)

        Parameters:
